author: Second Wind
description:
Dungeon Master and noted sandwich enthusiast Jack Packard, walks you through making a dungeon for Dungeons and Dragons (or which ever TTRPG you're using).
He'll be using a randomized room layout utilizing Dungeon Morph Dice https://dungeonmorphs.com/dice-sets/ and then expanding on the rooms to build a fully fleshed out dudgeon... with Draculas and everything!

Find the full map over at our Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

title: Let's Make a Dungeon Using Dice
